# SkyeIDEv2 Integrated Apps Suite

## Core Productivity Apps

1. **SkyeDocs** - Document editor with real-time collaboration, version control, and markdown support
2. **SkyeSheets** - Spreadsheet application with formulas, charts, and data visualization
3. **SkyeSlides** - Presentation tool with live collaboration and built-in templates

## Communication & Organization

4. **SkyeMail** - Email client with integrated inbox, calendar, and task management
5. **SkyeChat** - Team messaging with channels, threads, and file sharing
6. **SkyeCalendar** - Unified calendar with scheduling, meeting coordination, and reminders

## File Management & Storage

7. **SkyeDrive** - Cloud storage with file sync, sharing, and version history
8. **SkyeVault** - Secure password and credential management with team sharing

## Specialized Tools

9. **SkyeForms** - Survey and form builder with response analytics
10. **SkyeNotes** - Note-taking app with notebooks, tags, and web clipper
11. **SkyeAnalytics** - Data analysis and reporting dashboard for suite data
12. **SkyeTasks** - Project management and to-do list with Kanban boards

## Enterprise Features

13. **SkyeAdmin** - Centralized admin console for user management, permissions, and integrations

All apps would share: unified authentication, consistent UI, real-time sync, offline support, and mobile apps.

